                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Although I believe these truths to be self-evident, I also know they needed to be shared with those who might have felt tricked into thinking otherwise. At least you know one friend isn't out to get you this April Fools Day. Though you might want to look up from the paper instead of reading this as you walk through the quad.</p>
<p>You never know if you're about to be pranked-or see the nation's No. 1 recruit passing by.</p>
